FBIS3-20004 "drweu058_q_94008" FBIS-WEU-94-058 Document Type:Daily Report 24 Mar 1994 TURKEY Explosion at Grand Bazaar Injures 4 NC2403141994 Paris AFP in English 1043 GMT 24 Mar 94 NC2403141994 Paris AFP Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Istanbul, March 24 (AFP) -- A bomb explosion wounded four people Thursday [24 March] in Istanbul's Grand Bazaar, in the heart of the city's historic tourist district, in the second such attack in less than a week, police said. They said a Romanian was among the casualties from the blast which occurred in a ladies' toilet. On Saturday, an explosion in the Haydarpasa train station here left a Singaporian national wounded.
